Text: Who is Sivanantham?Sivananthamis a well-known software developer from Bangalore who is expert on various technologies and provides free education on online for under privileged students.Who is Mathan?Mathan is a friend of Sivanantham who Is also from software development and helps Siva in his social activities.Who is Vivek Narayan?Vivek is a cricket legend and he also writes poetries and inspire millions of young budding cricketers like Mugundhan, Dass Prakash and Chemical Karthik to follow their passions and dreams of becoming a cricketer.
